From cb2d8c31487dfe96b3f5c534e1d9fc63a1df6977 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Zhiyi Zhang <zzhang@codeweavers.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:13:36 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 59/65] dcomp: Implement DXGI_FORMAT_R8G8B8A8_UNORM surface
 conversion.

---
 dlls/dcomp/Makefile.in   |   2 +-
 dlls/dcomp/device.c      | 304 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/dcomp/surface.c     |   2 +-
 dlls/dcomp/tests/dcomp.c |  13 +-
 4 files changed, 312 insertions(+), 9 deletions(-)

